---
title: "performUpkeep (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_pause: check paused
    q_check_pause --> q_error_paused: paused == true
    q_error_paused --> [*]: revert "contract paused"
    q_check_pause --> q_check_role: paused == false

    q_check_role --> q_error_role: caller lacks AUCTION_WORKER_ROLE
    q_error_role --> [*]: revert "access denied"
    q_check_role --> q_check_asset_out: caller has AUCTION_WORKER_ROLE

    q_check_asset_out --> q_error_config: s_assetOut not configured
    q_error_config --> [*]: revert "asset out not configured"
    q_check_asset_out --> q_decode: s_assetOut configured

    q_decode --> q_process_starts: decode performData into (assetsToStart, assetsToEnd)

    q_process_starts --> q_iter_start: for asset in assetsToStart
    q_iter_start --> q_validate_asset: next asset
    q_iter_start --> q_process_ends: all starts processed

    q_validate_asset --> q_error_asset: asset not configured (hard revert)
    q_error_asset --> [*]: revert "asset not configured"
    q_validate_asset --> q_validate_prices: asset configured

    q_validate_prices --> q_error_price: assetOut price or asset price stale/zero (hard revert)
    q_error_price --> [*]: revert "invalid price"
    q_validate_prices --> q_validate_no_live: prices valid

    q_validate_no_live --> q_error_live: live auction exists (hard revert)
    q_error_live --> [*]: revert "auction already live"
    q_validate_no_live --> q_validate_min: no live auction

    q_validate_min --> q_error_min: totalUsdValue < minAuctionSizeUsd (hard revert)
    q_error_min --> [*]: revert "below minimum"
    q_validate_min --> q_start_auction: meets minimum

    q_start_auction --> q_pull: s_auctionStarts[asset] = block.timestamp
    q_pull --> q_approve: transferForSwap(feeAggregator, asset, amount)
    q_approve --> q_iter_start: approve(cowSwapVaultRelayer, amount)

    q_process_ends --> q_iter_end: for asset in assetsToEnd
    q_iter_end --> q_validate_end: next asset
    q_iter_end --> [*]: all ends processed

    q_validate_end --> q_error_no_auction: no live auction (hard revert)
    q_error_no_auction --> [*]: revert "no live auction"
    q_validate_end --> q_end_auction: auction exists

    q_end_auction --> q_return_assets: s_auctionStarts[asset] = 0
    q_return_assets --> q_send_proceeds: transfer remaining assets to FeeAggregator
    q_send_proceeds --> q_iter_end: transfer LINK proceeds to s_assetOutReceiver

    note right of q_start_auction
        INV-008: performUpkeep uses hard reverts for all validation (unlike checkUpkeep soft-skip)
        INV-009: auction start timestamp is set to block.timestamp
        INV-010: assets are pulled from FeeAggregator via SWAPPER_ROLE
        INV-011: on end, remaining assets return to FeeAggregator and LINK to Reserves
    end note
